RESEARCH ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This project implements methodologies from the following research work:

Schulman, J. & Thinking Machines Lab (2025). "LoRA Without Regret".
Thinking Machines Lab: Connectionism. DOI: 10.64434/tml.20250929
Available at: <https://thinkingmachines.ai/blog/lora/>

Users of this software should appropriately cite both:

1. This implementation (Ashioya Jotham Victor, 2025)
2. The original LoRA methodology (Schulman et al., 2025)

See README.md for citation formats and research acknowledgments.

